# Build artifacts — not tracked. Source lives in include/ (snippets), the
# fetched examples/ (pinned clone via the Makefile fetch-examples target), and
# xml/*.xml. Everything below is generated by `make`:
#   examples/     pinned example clone
#   xml/doc.mod   generated DocBook entity module (from xml/doc.mod.in)
#   xml/include/  htmlized source listings (from include/ + examples/)
#   html/         chunked HTML output (xsltproc)
examples/
xml/doc.mod
xml/include/
html/
